datastructures.heap

Class MaxArrayHeap<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • datastructures.heap.MaxArrayHeap<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - specifies the type of elements the max heap contains

    public class MaxArrayHeap<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>
extends java.lang.Object
    A max heap based on an array list. This max heap can also be used as a max-priority queue using MaxArrayHeapadd(Comparable) and MaxArrayHeappop()
    See Also:
    Min-Max-Heaps (Wikipedia)
